Central bank dollar / rouble rates 5362 / 5402 . The Russian Central Bank said it had set 5362 / 5402 roubles per dollar as its bid and offer rates for its operations on the currency market on Thursday . The official rate for Friday will be 5382 . On Wednesday the bid / offer rates were 5359 / 5399 , with the official dollar rate 5379 from Thursday . The Central Bank announces daily bid / offer dollar / rouble rates for its currency operations . The midpoint of these rates is the official dollar / rouble rate for the following day . The daily corridor for the rouble on the interbank market is 5219 / 5819 after 5216 / 5816 . - - Moscow Newsroom , + 7095 941 8520 
